flowchart TD
    A[Receive competing agent claims] --> B[Compute evidence quality]
    B --> C[Compute data completeness]
    C --> D[Compute recency score]
    D --> E[Compute intent-fit score]
    E --> F[Compute safety-bias score]
    F --> G[Weighted consensus score]
    G --> H{Score gap within merge threshold?}
    H -- No --> I[Select top claim]
    H -- Yes --> J{Secondary claim more conservative?}
    J -- No --> I
    J -- Yes --> K[Merge guardrail into winning action]
    I --> L[Suppress alternatives]
    K --> L
    L --> M[Generate final advice packet]
